title: Weird Food Combinations ( Michael Blackson)
itunes:title: Weird Food Combinations ( Michael Blackson)
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see what weird food combinations they eat after Saweetie was trending on socials because she poured ranch dressing on her spaghetti. Also, Michael Blackson and his bestfriend called in to speak about his new podcast, new comedy material and more. Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a spanish rapper that chopped off his roommates penis for social media.
